OL,6,F"He could not carry on anymore and
OL,7,Fsadly, there was not a safe and more
OL,8,Fcontrolled way for him to die.
OL,10,F"I know full well that if assisted
OL,11,Fdying was an option for him at that
OL,12,Ftime, he would have taken it because
OL,13,Fhe could've been surrounded by his
OL,14,Ffamily at the time that his life ended
OL,15,Fas opposed to sitting in his back
OL,16,Fgarden on his own."
