OL,6,FToday Gareth wanted to show his
OL,7,Fsupport as Labour MP Kim Leadbeater's
OL,8,Fintroduces a private members bill to
OL,9,Fthe House of Commons to offer
OL,10,Fterminally ill people choice at the
OL,11,Fend of life.
OL,13,FShe said there would be strict
OL,14,Feligibility criteria, including mental
OL,15,Fcompetence, assessment by two
OL,16,Findependent doctors and a cooling off
OL,17,Fperiod.
