OL,3,CSon calls for assisted dying reform
OL,4,Cafter father dies alone in garden
OL,6,FHigh profile supporters of legalising
OL,7,Fassisted dying include Dame Esther
OL,8,FRantzen who is terminally ill and
OL,9,Fwants to see the option "carefully
OL,10,Flegalised."
OL,12,FOthers, including the Archbishop of
OL,13,FCanterbury and Bishop Of Arundel and
OL,14,FBrighton, have expressed concerns
OL,15,Flegislation could put pressure on
OL,16,Fvulnerable people.
